<li><b>REname</b> possibly to Legal Professions or Lawyers.  I accept that the present title is ambiguous as implying either law-related professions or lawful occupations.  <a href="" title="User:Peterkingiron">Peterkingiron</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Peterkingiron">talk</a>) 23:01, 11 June 2009 (UTC)
<ul>
<li>Lawyers will not work in the name since not all of the occupations are lawyers. <a href="" title="User:Vegaswikian">Vegaswikian</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Vegaswikian">talk</a>) 19:00, 14 June 2009 (UTC)</li>
