<p>The <a href="" title="category:Rail transport designers">category:Rail transport designers</a> will have as subcategories “Fooland locomotive designers” ie by nationality and as well as Austrian, British German &#38; Swiss there should be American, Canadian, French and Italian locomotive designers; I suppose there would be someone from each of those countries. Are there engineers to justify a separate category by country for civil/construction/surveying and location engineers? 
