<li>I agree with the basic premise but oppose the choice of replacement categories. Why limit railroad engineering to locomotives? What about track planners, bridge engineers etc. ? <a href="" title="User:NVO">NVO</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:NVO">talk</a>) 07:58, 11 June 2009 (UTC)</li>
