<dd>I don&#39;t like mixing designers/builders because, to my mind, designers are people (albeit heads of teams) and builders are companies. To me <i>Locomotive builders</i> is synonymous with the existing and non-controversial <a href="" title="Category:Locomotive manufacturers">Category:Locomotive manufacturers</a>. <a href="" title="User:Globbet">Globbet</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Globbet">talk</a>) 16:05, 11 June 2009 (UTC)</dd></dl>
