<dd><i>The result of the discussion was:</i>  <b>Administrative close: category deleted as empty. However, I think there is consensus to implement <a href="" title="User:Andy Dingley">Andy Dingley</a>&#39;s proposal. I&#39;m not sure what was in the category, but anyone familiar with the articles can implement the suggestion at this point. (See also nomination immediately above.)</b> <a href="" title="User:Good Olfactory">Good Ol’factory</a> &#60;sup&#62;<a href="" title="User talk:Good Olfactory">(talk)</a>&#60;/sup&#62; 01:26, 24 June 2009 (UTC)</dd>
