<dd>
<ul>
<li>The most recent related cfd was perhaps <a href="#Category:Novels_by_Rich_Shapero" title="Wikipedia:Categories_for_discussion/Log/2009_March_14">this cfd in March 09</a>. <a href="" title="User:Occuli">Occuli</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Occuli">talk</a>) 21:48, 7 June 2009 (UTC)</li></ul></dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
