<li><b>Keep</b> - part of <a href="" title="Category:Books by author">Category:Books by author</a>. :: <a href="" title="User:Kevinalewis">&#60;span style=&#34;color: #33C;&#34;&#62;Kevinalewis&#60;/span&#62;</a> : <a href="" title="User talk:Kevinalewis">&#60;sup style=&#34;color:#C90&#34;&#62;(Talk Page)&#60;/sup&#62;</a>/<a href="" title="User:Kevinalewis/Desk">&#60;sub style=&#34;color:#C90&#34;&#62;(Desk)&#60;/sub&#62;</a> 10:10, 8 June 2009 (UTC)</li>
